#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Accounting:</strong> Full financial tracking and reporting."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Comptabilité :</strong> Suivi et reporting financiers complets."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Contacts:</strong> Maintain donor, community partner and customer\n"
"                    information."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Contacts :</strong> Conservez les informations des donateurs, "
"partenaires communautaires et clients."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Employees App:</strong>  Centralize information for all your staff "
"members and volunteers in one secure directory."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Application Employés :</strong> Centralisez les informations de tous "
"vos membres du personnel et bénévoles dans un répertoire sécurisé unique."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Inventory:</strong> Gain deeper insight into donation stock and "
"turnover."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Inventaire :</strong> Obtenez une meilleure visibilité sur les "
"stocks provenant des dons et sur la rotation."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Keep shifts balanced:</strong> Plan employee coverage across peak "
"hours\n"
"                    (weekends, donation drive days)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Maintenez un équilibre des postes :</strong> Planifiez la couverture "
"du personnel durant les heures de pointe (week-ends, journées de collecte)."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Leaves:</strong> Easily manage employee's time off and plan work\n"
"                    accordingly."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Congés :</strong> Gérez facilement les congés du personnel et "
"planifiez le travail en conséquence."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Leverage promotions:</strong> Use Odoo POS’s discount and pricing "
"rules\n"
"                    for events like “fill a bag” sales."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Profitez des promotions :</strong> Utilisez les règles de remise et "
"de tarification du PdV Odoo pour des événements tels que les ventes \"tout "
"ce qui rentre dans le sac\"."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Planning App:</strong> Organize shifts and schedules easily, "
"ensuring you always have enough hands on deck for sorting and sales."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Application Planification :</strong> Gérez simplement les horaires "
"et les postes afin d’avoir en permanence le personnel nécessaire pour le tri "
"et la vente."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Point of Sale App:</strong> Process transactions quickly with a "
"flexible checkout system that supports sales by product, fixed amount, or "
"weight."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Application Point de vente :</strong> Traitez rapidement les "
"transactions grâce à un système d’encaissement flexible qui prend en charge "
"les ventes par produit, par montant fixe ou au poids."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Purchase:</strong> Manage store supply needs (bags, hangers, "
"cleaning\n"
"                    supplies)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Achats :</strong> Gérez les besoins en fournitures du magasin (sacs, "
"cintres, produits de nettoyage)."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Standardize categories:</strong> Use consistent product categories "
"(e.g.,\n"
"                    clothing, books, household) to keep reporting clear."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Standardisez les catégories :</strong> Utilisez des catégories de "
"produits cohérentes (p. ex. vêtements, livres, articles ménagers) afin de "
"garder un reporting clair."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Train your staff:</strong> Volunteers and part-time staff pick up "
"faster\n"
"                    with Odoo’s intuitive POS interface."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Formez votre personnel :</strong> Les bénévoles et employés à temps "
"partiel apprennent plus rapidement grâce à l’interface intuitive du PdV Odoo."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Website:</strong> Showcase your mission and events online."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Site Web :</strong> Présentez votre mission et vos événements en "
"ligne."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>eCommerce:</strong> Sell select high-value items online to reach "
"wider\n"
"                    audiences."
msgstr ""
"<strong>eCommerce :</strong> Vendez en ligne certains articles de grande "
"valeur pour toucher un public plus large."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model:product.template,name:thrift_store.product_template_12
msgid "Accessories"
msgstr "Accessoires"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add a product to the order, 10 for example, and adjust the count per the\n"
"                        number of pieces with that price in the customer "
"basket!"
msgstr ""
"Ajoutez un produit à la commande, 10 par exemple, et ajustez le nombre selon "
"le nombre de pièces à ce prix dans le panier du client !"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the product labelled By Weight and adjust the quantity per measured\n"
"                        weight"
msgstr ""
"Ajoutez le produit intitulé Au poids et ajustez la quantité selon le poids "
"mesuré"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust the shift time, specify the role and save it"
msgstr "Ajustez l’heure du shift, indiquez le rôle et enregistrez-le"

