#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click on the planning to add a new shift"
msgstr "Cliquez sur le planning pour ajouter un nouveau shift"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Découvrez-en plus sur Odoo en vous plongeant dans notre"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to\n"
"            improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"Découvrez les bases de ce pack et explorez toutes les possibilités qu’Odoo "
"offre pour\n"
"            améliorer votre expérience."

